# GitLab Duo Pro License & Code Review Workflow

## 1. Product Overview & Core Licensing Details
**GitLab Duo Pro** is a paid AI add-on subscription providing advanced capabilities like Code Suggestions, agentic chat, and automatic code reviews.

*   **Prerequisites:** Requires an active paid **GitLab Premium** or **GitLab Ultimate** base subscription. It cannot be added to a GitLab Free tier subscription.
*   **Pricing:** Costs **\$19 per user per month**.
*   **Seat Assignment:** It is a seat-based add-on license. Group owners or administrators must explicitly purchase and assign Duo Pro seats to the specific users who need access.
*   **Deployment Options:** Supported across GitLab SaaS (GitLab.com), Self-Managed, and GitLab Dedicated environments.
*   **Official FAQ:** For underlying billing queries, review the [GitLab Licensing and Subscription FAQ](https://gitlab.com).

